---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="brain begging for sugar" description="the bottleneck used to be building and grinding. now its inverted.">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-faint mb-4">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">writing</a> <span class="text-faint">/</span> brain-begging-for-sugar
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal animate-fade-up">brain begging for sugar</h1>

    <div class="essay mt-10 animate-fade-up delay-1">
      <p>builder normal day use to fill with fixing css this, changing the state that. and like 2-3 big architectural decisions by the end of the day.</p>

      <hr class="my-12 border-border" />

      <p>now its inverted. agent done those in minutes. judgement per day skyrocketed.</p>

      <p class="mt-6 text-spice">leave your brain begging for sugar.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-6 border-t border-border">
      <a href="/writing" class="text-spice hover:underline">← back to writing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .essay p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
